00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:07,460
You're the top idiot!

857
00:35:07,700 --> 00:35:09,660
No. You're too dumb
to even be the dumbest.

858
00:35:10,820 --> 00:35:12,020
Then who outranks me, Tongdao?

859
00:35:14,140 --> 00:35:14,780
I...

860
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:21,100
[Shanghai North]

861
00:35:21,340 --> 00:35:22,220
If it weren't for you all,

862
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:23,300
I might never have seen

863
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:24,420
Natasha in this lifetime.

864
00:35:24,420 --> 00:35:25,020
Thank you.

865
00:35:25,780 --> 00:35:26,500
Thanks

866
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:28,180
for playing along.

867
00:35:29,220 --> 00:35:31,540
I've been putting on a show
since I hit Shanghai.

868
00:35:32,100 --> 00:35:34,420
This little bit of drama is nothing.

869
00:35:35,060 --> 00:35:35,940
Glebov,

870
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:37,460
we should get on the train.

871
00:35:38,020 --> 00:35:40,060
I'm going to see my Natasha.

872
00:35:40,620 --> 00:35:42,260
Hope you and your daughter
can reunite soon.

873
00:35:42,540 --> 00:35:43,860
Thank you, Miss Chu.

874
00:35:43,860 --> 00:35:46,260
And I wish you and Mr. Wen
a prosperous business.

875
00:35:47,100 --> 00:35:49,740
I hope to have the opportunity
to meet you again.

876
00:35:53,460 --> 00:35:54,100
Farewell.

877
00:35:55,380 --> 00:35:56,140
Farewell.

878
00:35:56,140 --> 00:35:57,020
Have a safe journey,

879
00:35:57,220 --> 00:35:57,820
Mr. Yang.

880
00:35:59,060 --> 00:35:59,660
Please.

881
00:36:01,620 --> 00:36:02,180
I'm off.

882
00:36:02,540 --> 00:36:02,980
Alright.

883
00:36:02,980 --> 00:36:03,660
Come back soon.

884
00:36:04,540 --> 00:36:05,460
You understand Russian?

885
00:36:07,380 --> 00:36:08,100
I don't.

886
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:09,820
But nodding usually does the trick.

887
00:36:17,460 --> 00:36:18,900
I was key

888
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:20,300
to beating Mr. Tian this time.

889
00:36:22,100 --> 00:36:23,060
Here to take credit, are we?

890
00:36:23,740 --> 00:36:24,820
I also want a reward.

891
00:36:25,580 --> 00:36:28,100
Mr. Wen, how do you plan to reward me?

892
00:36:28,100 --> 00:36:29,020
I'll treat you to a meal.

893
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:32,860
You really think one meal
covers everything I did?

894
00:36:34,060 --> 00:36:35,260
I'll also give you some bonus money.

895
00:36:36,380 --> 00:36:37,060
How much?

896
00:36:37,740 --> 00:36:38,540
One hundred silver dollars.

897
00:36:39,860 --> 00:36:40,900
Isn't that too little?

898
00:36:42,020 --> 00:36:43,100
Then how much do you want?

899
00:36:43,340 --> 00:36:44,420
I want a promotion.

900
00:36:44,420 --> 00:36:46,740
I don't want to be just another manager.

901
00:36:46,740 --> 00:36:48,020
I want to be Deputy General Manager.

902
00:36:48,020 --> 00:36:48,940
Deputy General Manager?

903
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:51,140
You've only just started here.

904
00:36:51,580 --> 00:36:53,860
I also want to convert
my one-tenth labor stock

905
00:36:53,860 --> 00:36:54,860
into capital stock.

906
00:36:56,380 --> 00:36:57,620
We can talk about the promotion,

907
00:36:57,620 --> 00:36:58,420
but the capital stock...

908
00:36:59,580 --> 00:37:01,140
Given my abilities,

909
00:37:01,140 --> 00:37:02,580
I'm more than qualified
to be the Deputy General Manager.

910
00:37:02,580 --> 00:37:04,300
And considering what I've done
for Wen's Pharmacy,

911
00:37:04,300 --> 00:37:05,100
I've earned
a tenth of the capital stock.

912
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:06,540
Alright, how about this?

913
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:08,700
I'll get you promoted
and give you a raise.

914
00:37:08,700 --> 00:37:09,660
We'll come back

915
00:37:10,380 --> 00:37:11,020
to the capital stock later.

916
00:37:14,620 --> 00:37:16,220
Then Mr. Wen, I think I'll resign.

917
00:37:16,580 --> 00:37:17,420
After the whole Mr. Tian situation,

918
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:19,060
I wouldn't be surprised

919
00:37:19,220 --> 00:37:20,620
if pharmacies all over Shanghai

920
00:37:20,620 --> 00:37:21,940
are lining up to hire me.

921
00:37:26,500 --> 00:37:27,420
Are you threatening me?

922
00:37:27,580 --> 00:37:28,140
Yes, I am.

923
00:37:33,980 --> 00:37:34,660
Alright then.

924
00:37:36,740 --> 00:37:38,540
If you want to convert
your labor stock into capital stock,

925
00:37:38,780 --> 00:37:40,180
then I cannot give you a raise.

926
00:37:40,460 --> 00:37:41,140
Also,

927
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:42,900
if you want to do the work
of a Deputy General Manager,

928
00:37:43,180 --> 00:37:44,580
you can only get paid
like an ordinary manager.

929
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:45,620
Can you do that?

930
00:37:47,340 --> 00:37:48,020
Deal.

931
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:52,660
And you have to treat me to dinner.

932
00:37:53,060 --> 00:37:53,860
Just one meal.

933
00:37:54,460 --> 00:37:55,500
I'll choose the restaurant.

934
00:37:55,700 --> 00:37:56,460
I'll order the dishes.

935
00:37:56,700 --> 00:37:57,580
You pay for the wine.

936
00:37:57,580 --> 00:37:58,580
The tip is on you.

937
00:38:02,180 --> 00:38:04,060
You calculating woman.

938
00:38:04,780 --> 00:38:05,980
What's that?

939
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:07,460
It means very calculating.

940
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,820
You're saying I'm a calculating woman?

941
00:38:09,060 --> 00:38:09,860
Aren't you?

942
00:38:11,060 --> 00:38:12,660
The feeling is mutual, Mr. Wen.

943
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:26,940
You're home?
Why didn't you turn on the light?

944
00:38:28,060 --> 00:38:28,780
What's wrong?

945
00:38:31,900 --> 00:38:33,180
I just realized

946
00:38:34,300 --> 00:38:36,260
that the Tian family never accepted me.

947
00:38:37,580 --> 00:38:38,940
They just wanted to use me

948
00:38:40,020 --> 00:38:40,700
against you.

949
00:38:44,620 --> 00:38:45,780
Inviting me to their table,

950
00:38:46,660 --> 00:38:48,060
asking me for afternoon tea,

951
00:38:48,820 --> 00:38:50,620
and letting me overhear
Huang Deming getting fired.

952
00:38:51,900 --> 00:38:53,860
It was all set up.

953
00:38:54,820 --> 00:38:55,460
Yes.

954
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:59,020
Mr. Tian anticipated

955
00:38:59,980 --> 00:39:01,980
that you would tip me off.

956
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:03,860
So he set a trap

957
00:39:03,860 --> 00:39:05,020
for both of us.

958
00:39:08,940 --> 00:39:09,620
Thankfully,

959
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:11,500
you didn't fall for it.

960
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,180
Otherwise,

961
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,740
I'd never be able to live with myself.

962
00:39:20,500 --> 00:39:22,300
How did you know it was a trap?

963
00:39:23,140 --> 00:39:24,100
Remember this?

964
00:39:24,340 --> 00:39:26,340
Back when I just joined Wen's Pharmacy,

965
00:39:26,500 --> 00:39:29,100
you introduced me to Tian's Apothecary
to discuss a partnership.

966
00:39:30,380 --> 00:39:31,140
I remember.

967
00:39:31,820 --> 00:39:33,060
When you came back,

968
00:39:33,420 --> 00:39:35,420
you just said it didn't work out.

969
00:39:37,020 --> 00:39:38,180
It wasn't just a fallout.

970
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:41,700
Mr. Tian totally humiliated me.

971
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:42,900
Oh my goodness.

972
00:39:43,220 --> 00:39:46,020
From the way he treated me,

973
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:47,620
I could tell

974
00:39:48,100 --> 00:39:49,140
they had

975
00:39:49,140 --> 00:39:51,180
serious issues with you.

976
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:52,660
But at that time,

977
00:39:52,660 --> 00:39:54,380
you and Mr. Tian were deeply in love,

978
00:39:54,780 --> 00:39:56,180
and I didn't want to spoil your mood,

979
00:39:56,180 --> 00:39:57,260
so I didn't tell you.

980
00:39:59,140 --> 00:40:00,340
I'm sorry, Shaohua.

981
00:40:01,140 --> 00:40:01,860
Later,

982
00:40:02,100 --> 00:40:04,460
Tian Tongdao sued Wen's Pharmacy.

983
00:40:04,660 --> 00:40:05,660
And at this critical moment,

984
00:40:06,100 --> 00:40:08,100
they suddenly accepted you.

985
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:09,660
This completely contradicts

986
00:40:09,660 --> 00:40:11,540
his harsh and snobbish style.

987
00:40:12,020 --> 00:40:13,620
It made me suspect

988
00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:15,540
their intention in accepting you.

989
00:40:16,380 --> 00:40:17,220
And then later,

990
00:40:17,540 --> 00:40:19,100
at the most critical point
of the lawsuit,

991
00:40:19,580 --> 00:40:21,140
they allowed you,
who were visiting for the first time,

992
00:40:21,140 --> 00:40:22,860
to overhear such private conversations.

993
00:40:24,220 --> 00:40:25,580
That made me even more suspicious.

994
00:40:25,740 --> 00:40:26,700
Didn't your friend say

995
00:40:26,700 --> 00:40:28,780
Mr. Tian fired Claudy's assistant?

996
00:40:29,540 --> 00:40:31,220
Maybe we can get him on our side.

997
00:40:32,340 --> 00:40:33,460
That could work.

998
00:40:33,620 --> 00:40:34,820
It might not be a way out

999
00:40:35,340 --> 00:40:36,140
but a trap.

1000
00:40:36,460 --> 00:40:37,100
Why?

1001
00:40:38,740 --> 00:40:39,460
Intuition.

1002
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:41,060
Does that count?

1003
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:44,100
Well, I trust Miss Chu's judgment.

1004
00:40:48,220 --> 00:40:49,100
I'm so foolish.

1005
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:50,300
You're not foolish.

1006
00:40:50,980 --> 00:40:53,140
You just get flustered when you care.

1007
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:56,060
And you wanted to marry
Mr. Tian so much,

1008
00:40:56,060 --> 00:40:57,980
yet when we were at odds with them,

1009
00:40:57,980 --> 00:40:59,340
you were still willing to help me.

1010
00:40:59,580 --> 00:41:01,220
The info may have been wrong,

1011
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:03,580
but your sincerity was never in doubt.

1012
00:41:03,820 --> 00:41:05,340
So Erniu, I should thank you.

1013
00:41:05,820 --> 00:41:08,580
I might've done more harm than good.

1014
00:41:08,580 --> 00:41:09,700
Not at all.

1015
00:41:09,900 --> 00:41:11,700
Your concern made a real difference.

1016
00:41:12,060 --> 00:41:13,940
The moment we realized
Mr. Tian was using you

1017
00:41:13,940 --> 00:41:15,180
to bait us,

1018
00:41:15,460 --> 00:41:17,420
we devised a way to turn the tables.

1019
00:41:18,060 --> 00:41:18,860
I was thinking

1020
00:41:18,860 --> 00:41:22,180
if Mr. Tian fired Huang Deming

1021
00:41:22,580 --> 00:41:25,260
to put on a show for us,

1022
00:41:25,580 --> 00:41:28,340
then what was the purpose of that?

1023
00:41:28,660 --> 00:41:30,100
He must have also believed

1024
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:32,340
