1027
00:41:36,020 --> 00:41:38,100
Then pushing Huang Deming to us

1028
00:41:38,460 --> 00:41:41,140
must be to cause destruction

1029
00:41:41,420 --> 00:41:42,700
under the guise of defecting.

1030
00:41:42,900 --> 00:41:44,100
That makes some sense.

1031
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:45,700
No matter what they do,

1032
00:41:46,140 --> 00:41:46,980
just ignore them.

1033
00:41:47,460 --> 00:41:49,620
Just have Mr. Yang find
a few more people to testify in court.

1034
00:41:49,620 --> 00:41:51,580
The presiding judge will believe us.

1035
00:41:51,860 --> 00:41:54,780
Let's go talk to Huang.

1036
00:41:55,020 --> 00:41:56,340
With enough money on the table,

1037
00:41:56,340 --> 00:41:57,900
