1038
00:41:58,900 --> 00:42:01,140
Why not go against the grain?

1039
00:42:02,020 --> 00:42:03,300
Glebov

1040
00:42:03,780 --> 00:42:05,700
looks like a scholar,

1041
00:42:06,260 --> 00:42:08,060
and he speaks English very well.

1042
00:42:08,060 --> 00:42:09,060
He also knows some medicine.

1043
00:42:09,060 --> 00:42:11,660
That's why Mr. Tian chose him

1044
00:42:11,660 --> 00:42:13,500
and had him impersonate
an American professor.

1045
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:14,780
Over the past two years,

1046
00:42:14,780 --> 00:42:16,780
he's poured a lot of money

1047
00:42:16,940 --> 00:42:18,940
into boosting Claudy's reputation.

1048
00:42:19,660 --> 00:42:21,860
So why must we expose him

1049
00:42:22,220 --> 00:42:23,140
