1052
00:42:29,300 --> 00:42:30,780
The lawsuit isn't the goal.

1053
00:42:31,300 --> 00:42:32,180
The market is.

1054
00:42:33,420 --> 00:42:35,580
If we can make use of it,

1055
00:42:35,580 --> 00:42:38,740
